07228            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07229     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>&
07230     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07231     operator=(const _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>& __x)
07232     {
07233       if (this != &__x)
07234  {
07235 
07236    clear();
07237    _M_impl._M_key_compare = __x._M_impl._M_key_compare;
07238    if (__x._M_root() != 0)
07239      {
07240        _M_root() = _M_copy(__x._M_begin(), _M_end());
07241        _M_leftmost() = _S_minimum(_M_root());
07242        _M_rightmost() = _S_maximum(_M_root());
07243        _M_impl._M_node_count = __x._M_impl._M_node_count;
07244      }
07245  }
07246       return *this;
07247     }

07253     _M_insert(_Base_ptr __x, _Base_ptr __p, const _Val& __v)
07254     {
07255       bool __insert_left = (__x != 0 || __p == _M_end()
07256        || _M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v),
07257             _S_key(__p)));
07258 
07259       _Link_type __z = _M_create_node(__v);
07260 
07261       _Rb_tree_insert_and_rebalance(__insert_left, __z, __p,
07262         this->_M_impl._M_header);
07263       ++_M_impl._M_node_count;

07307     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07308     _M_insert_equal(const _Val& __v)
07309     {
07310       _Link_type __x = _M_begin();
07311       _Link_type __y = _M_end();
07312       while (__x != 0)
07313  {
07314    __y = __x;
07315    __x = _M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v), _S_key(__x)) ?
07316          _S_left(__x) : _S_right(__x);
07317  }
07318       return _M_insert(__x, __y, __v);

07338   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KeyOfValue,
07339            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07340     void
07341     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07342     swap(_Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>& __t)
07343     {
07344       if (_M_root() == 0)
07345  {
07346    if (__t._M_root() != 0)
07347      {
07348        _M_root() = __t._M_root();
07349        _M_leftmost() = __t._M_leftmost();
07350        _M_rightmost() = __t._M_rightmost();
07351        _M_root()->_M_parent = _M_end();
07352 
07353        __t._M_root() = 0;
07354        __t._M_leftmost() = __t._M_end();
07355        __t._M_rightmost() = __t._M_end();
07356      }
07357  }
07358       else if (__t._M_root() == 0)
07359  {
07360    __t._M_root() = _M_root();
07361    __t._M_leftmost() = _M_leftmost();
07362    __t._M_rightmost() = _M_rightmost();
07363    __t._M_root()->_M_parent = __t._M_end();
07364 
07365    _M_root() = 0;
07366    _M_leftmost() = _M_end();
07367    _M_rightmost() = _M_end();
07368  }
07369       else
07370  {
07371    std::swap(_M_root(),__t._M_root());
07372    std::swap(_M_leftmost(),__t._M_leftmost());
07373    std::swap(_M_rightmost(),__t._M_rightmost());
07374 
07375    _M_root()->_M_parent = _M_end();
07376    __t._M_root()->_M_parent = __t._M_end();
07377  }
07378 
07379       std::swap(this->_M_impl._M_node_count, __t._M_impl._M_node_count);
07380       std::swap(this->_M_impl._M_key_compare, __t._M_impl._M_key_compare);
07381 
07382 
07383 
07384       std::__alloc_swap<_Node_allocator>::
07385  _S_do_it(_M_get_Node_allocator(), __t._M_get_Node_allocator());
07386     }

07388   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KeyOfValue,
07389            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07390     pair<typename _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue,
07391       _Compare, _Alloc>::iterator, bool>
07392     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07393     _M_insert_unique(const _Val& __v)
07394     {
07395       _Link_type __x = _M_begin();
07396       _Link_type __y = _M_end();
07397       bool __comp = true;
07398       while (__x != 0)
07399  {
07400    __y = __x;
07401    __comp = _M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v), _S_key(__x));
07402    __x = __comp ? _S_left(__x) : _S_right(__x);
07403  }
07404       iterator __j = iterator(__y);
07405       if (__comp)
07406  if (__j == begin())
07407    return pair<iterator,bool>(_M_insert(__x, __y, __v), true);
07408  else
07409    --__j;
07410       if (_M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key(__j._M_node), _KeyOfValue()(__v)))
07411  return pair<iterator, bool>(_M_insert(__x, __y, __v), true);
07412       return pair<iterator, bool>(__j, false);
07413     }

07415   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KeyOfValue,
07416            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07417     typename _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::iterator
07418     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07419     _M_insert_unique(iterator __position, const _Val& __v)
07420     {
07421 
07422       if (__position._M_node == _M_end())
07423  {
07424    if (size() > 0
07425        && _M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key(_M_rightmost()),
07426      _KeyOfValue()(__v)))
07427      return _M_insert(0, _M_rightmost(), __v);
07428    else
07429      return _M_insert_unique(__v).first;
07430  }
07431       else if (_M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v),
07432           _S_key(__position._M_node)))
07433  {
07434 
07435    iterator __before = __position;
07436    if (__position._M_node == _M_leftmost())
07437      return _M_insert(_M_leftmost(), _M_leftmost(), __v);
07438    else if (_M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key((--__before)._M_node),
07439        _KeyOfValue()(__v)))
07440      {
07441        if (_S_right(__before._M_node) == 0)
07442   return _M_insert(0, __before._M_node, __v);
07443        else
07444   return _M_insert(__position._M_node,
07445      __position._M_node, __v);
07446      }
07447    else
07448      return _M_insert_unique(__v).first;
07449  }
07450       else if (_M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key(__position._M_node),
07451           _KeyOfValue()(__v)))
07452  {
07453 
07454    iterator __after = __position;
07455    if (__position._M_node == _M_rightmost())
07456      return _M_insert(0, _M_rightmost(), __v);
07457    else if (_M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v),
07458        _S_key((++__after)._M_node)))
07459      {
07460        if (_S_right(__position._M_node) == 0)
07461   return _M_insert(0, __position._M_node, __v);
07462        else
07463   return _M_insert(__after._M_node, __after._M_node, __v);
07464      }
07465    else
07466      return _M_insert_unique(__v).first;
07467  }
07468       else
07469  return __position;
07470     }

07529   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KeyOfValue,
07530            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07531     typename _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::iterator
07532     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07533     _M_insert_equal(iterator __position, const _Val& __v)
07534     {
07535 
07536       if (__position._M_node == _M_end())
07537  {
07538    if (size() > 0
07539        && !_M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v),
07540       _S_key(_M_rightmost())))
07541      return _M_insert(0, _M_rightmost(), __v);
07542    else
07543      return _M_insert_equal(__v);
07544  }
07545       else if (!_M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key(__position._M_node),
07546            _KeyOfValue()(__v)))
07547  {
07548 
07549    iterator __before = __position;
07550    if (__position._M_node == _M_leftmost())
07551      return _M_insert(_M_leftmost(), _M_leftmost(), __v);
07552    else if (!_M_impl._M_key_compare(_KeyOfValue()(__v),
07553         _S_key((--__before)._M_node)))
07554      {
07555        if (_S_right(__before._M_node) == 0)
07556   return _M_insert(0, __before._M_node, __v);
07557        else
07558   return _M_insert(__position._M_node,
07559      __position._M_node, __v);
07560      }
07561    else
07562      return _M_insert_equal(__v);
07563  }
07564       else
07565  {
07566 
07567    iterator __after = __position;
07568    if (__position._M_node == _M_rightmost())
07569      return _M_insert(0, _M_rightmost(), __v);
07570    else if (!_M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key((++__after)._M_node),
07571         _KeyOfValue()(__v)))
07572      {
07573        if (_S_right(__position._M_node) == 0)
07574   return _M_insert(0, __position._M_node, __v);
07575        else
07576   return _M_insert(__after._M_node, __after._M_node, __v);
07577      }
07578    else
07579      return _M_insert_equal_lower(__v);
07580  }
07581     }

07687   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KeyOfValue,
07688            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07689     typename _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::size_type
07690     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KeyOfValue, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07691     erase(const _Key& __x)
07692     {
07693       pair<iterator, iterator> __p = equal_range(__x);
07694       const size_type __old_size = size();
07695       erase(__p.first, __p.second);
07696       return __old_size - size();
07697     }

07699   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KoV,
07700            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07701     typename _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KoV, _Compare, _Alloc>::_Link_type
07702     _Rb_tree<_Key, _Val, _KoV, _Compare, _Alloc>::
07703     _M_copy(_Const_Link_type __x, _Link_type __p)
07704     {
07705 
07706       _Link_type __top = _M_clone_node(__x);
07707       __top->_M_parent = __p;
07708 
07709       try
07710  {
07711    if (__x->_M_right)
07712      __top->_M_right = _M_copy(_S_right(__x), __top);
07713    __p = __top;
07714    __x = _S_left(__x);
07715 
07716    while (__x != 0)
07717      {
07718        _Link_type __y = _M_clone_node(__x);
07719        __p->_M_left = __y;
07720        __y->_M_parent = __p;
07721        if (__x->_M_right)
07722   __y->_M_right = _M_copy(_S_right(__x), __y);
07723        __p = __y;
07724        __x = _S_left(__x);
07725      }
07726  }
07727       catch(...)
07728  {
07729    _M_erase(__top);
07730    throw;
07731  }
07732       return __top;
07733     }

07934   unsigned int
07935   _Rb_tree_black_count(const _Rb_tree_node_base* __node,
07936                        const _Rb_tree_node_base* __root);
07937 
07938   template<typename _Key, typename _Val, typename _KeyOfValue,
07939            typename _Compare, typename _Alloc>
07940     bool
07941     _Rb_tree<_Key,_Val,_KeyOfValue,_Compare,_Alloc>::__rb_verify() const
07942     {
07943       if (_M_impl._M_node_count == 0 || begin() == end())
07944  return _M_impl._M_node_count == 0 && begin() == end()
07945         && this->_M_impl._M_header._M_left == _M_end()
07946         && this->_M_impl._M_header._M_right == _M_end();
07947 
07948       unsigned int __len = _Rb_tree_black_count(_M_leftmost(), _M_root());
07949       for (const_iterator __it = begin(); __it != end(); ++__it)
07950  {
07951    _Const_Link_type __x = static_cast<_Const_Link_type>(__it._M_node);
07952    _Const_Link_type __L = _S_left(__x);
07953    _Const_Link_type __R = _S_right(__x);
07954 
07955    if (__x->_M_color == _S_red)
07956      if ((__L && __L->_M_color == _S_red)
07957   || (__R && __R->_M_color == _S_red))
07958        return false;
07959 
07960    if (__L && _M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key(__x), _S_key(__L)))
07961      return false;
07962    if (__R && _M_impl._M_key_compare(_S_key(__R), _S_key(__x)))
07963      return false;
07964 
07965    if (!__L && !__R && _Rb_tree_black_count(__x, _M_root()) != __len)
07966      return false;
07967  }
07968 
07969       if (_M_leftmost() != _Rb_tree_node_base::_S_minimum(_M_root()))
07970  return false;
07971       if (_M_rightmost() != _Rb_tree_node_base::_S_maximum(_M_root()))
07972  return false;
07973       return true;
07974     }

10828   typedef unsigned long _Bit_type;
10829   enum { _S_word_bit = int(8 * sizeof(_Bit_type)) };
10830 
10831   struct _Bit_reference
10832   {
10833     _Bit_type * _M_p;
10834     _Bit_type _M_mask;
10835 
10836     _Bit_reference(_Bit_type * __x, _Bit_type __y)
10837     : _M_p(__x), _M_mask(__y) { }
10838 
10839     _Bit_reference() : _M_p(0), _M_mask(0) { }
10840 
10841     operator bool() const
10842     { return !!(*_M_p & _M_mask); }
10843 
10844     _Bit_reference&
10845     operator=(bool __x)
10846     {
10847       if (__x)
10848  *_M_p |= _M_mask;
10849       else
10850  *_M_p &= ~_M_mask;
10851       return *this;
10852     }
10853 
10854     _Bit_reference&
10855     operator=(const _Bit_reference& __x)
10856     { return *this = bool(__x); }
10857 
10858     bool
10859     operator==(const _Bit_reference& __x) const
10860     { return bool(*this) == bool(__x); }
10861 
10862     bool
10863     operator<(const _Bit_reference& __x) const
10864     { return !bool(*this) && bool(__x); }
10865 
10866     void
10867     flip()
10868     { *_M_p ^= _M_mask; }
10869   };

10871   struct _Bit_iterator_base
10872   : public std::iterator<std::random_access_iterator_tag, bool>
10873   {
10874     _Bit_type * _M_p;
10875     unsigned int _M_offset;
10876 
10877     _Bit_iterator_base(_Bit_type * __x, unsigned int __y)
10878     : _M_p(__x), _M_offset(__y) { }
10879 
10880     void
10881     _M_bump_up()
10882     {
10883       if (_M_offset++ == int(_S_word_bit) - 1)
10884  {
10885    _M_offset = 0;
10886    ++_M_p;
10887  }
10888     }
10889 
10890     void
10891     _M_bump_down()
10892     {
10893       if (_M_offset-- == 0)
10894  {
10895    _M_offset = int(_S_word_bit) - 1;
10896    --_M_p;
10897  }
10898     }
10899 
10900     void
10901     _M_incr(ptrdiff_t __i)
10902     {
10903       difference_type __n = __i + _M_offset;
10904       _M_p += __n / int(_S_word_bit);
10905       __n = __n % int(_S_word_bit);
10906       if (__n < 0)
10907  {
10908    __n += int(_S_word_bit);
10909    --_M_p;
10910  }
10911       _M_offset = static_cast<unsigned int>(__n);
10912     }
10913 
10914     bool
10915     operator==(const _Bit_iterator_base& __i) const
10916     { return _M_p == __i._M_p && _M_offset == __i._M_offset; }
10917 
10918     bool
10919     operator<(const _Bit_iterator_base& __i) const
10920     {
10921       return _M_p < __i._M_p
10922       || (_M_p == __i._M_p && _M_offset < __i._M_offset);
10923     }
10924 
10925     bool
10926     operator!=(const _Bit_iterator_base& __i) const
10927     { return !(*this == __i); }
10928 
10929     bool
10930     operator>(const _Bit_iterator_base& __i) const
10931     { return __i < *this; }
10932 
10933     bool
10934     operator<=(const _Bit_iterator_base& __i) const
10935     { return !(__i < *this); }
10936 
10937     bool
10938     operator>=(const _Bit_iterator_base& __i) const
10939     { return !(*this < __i); }
10940   };
10941 
10942   inline ptrdiff_t
10943   operator-(const _Bit_iterator_base& __x, const _Bit_iterator_base& __y)
10944   {
10945     return (int(_S_word_bit) * (__x._M_p - __y._M_p)
10946      + __x._M_offset - __y._M_offset);
10947   }

10949   struct _Bit_iterator : public _Bit_iterator_base
10950   {
10951     typedef _Bit_reference reference;
10952     typedef _Bit_reference* pointer;
10953     typedef _Bit_iterator iterator;
10954 
10955     _Bit_iterator() : _Bit_iterator_base(0, 0) { }
10956 
10957     _Bit_iterator(_Bit_type * __x, unsigned int __y)
10958     : _Bit_iterator_base(__x, __y) { }
10959 
10960     reference
10961     operator*() const
10962     { return reference(_M_p, 1UL << _M_offset); }
10963 
10964     iterator&
10965     operator++()
10966     {
10967       _M_bump_up();
10968       return *this;
10969     }
10970 
10971     iterator
10972     operator++(int)
10973     {
10974       iterator __tmp = *this;
10975       _M_bump_up();
10976       return __tmp;
10977     }
10978 
10979     iterator&
10980     operator--()
10981     {
10982       _M_bump_down();

11647     {

11654    std::fill(__position, __position + difference_type(__n), __x);

11660    _Bit_type * __q = this->_M_allocate(__len);
11661    iterator __i = _M_copy_aligned(begin(), __position,
11662       iterator(__q, 0));
11663    std::fill(__i, __i + difference_type(__n), __x);
11664    this->_M_impl._M_finish = std::copy(__position, end(),
11665            __i + difference_type(__n));
11666    this->_M_deallocate();
11667    this->_M_impl._M_end_of_storage = (__q + ((__len
11668            + int(_S_word_bit) - 1)
11669           / int(_S_word_bit)));

12311    ;
12312    Map_Iter miter = _index.find( key );
12313    if( miter == _index.end() ) return false;
12314    if( touch_data )
12315      _touch( key );
12316    data = miter->second->second;
12317    return true;
12318   }
12319 
12320 
12321 
12322 
12323 
12324 
12325   inline void insert( const Key &key, const Data &data ) {
12326    ;
12327 
12328    Map_Iter miter = _touch( key );
12329    if( miter != _index.end() )
12330     _remove( miter );
12331 
12332 
12333    _list.push_front( std::make_pair( key, data ) );
12334    List_Iter liter = _list.begin();
12335 
12336 
12337    _index.insert( std::make_pair( key, liter ) );
12338    _curr_size += Sizefn()( data );
12339 
12340 
12341    while( _curr_size > _max_size ) {
12342 
12343     liter = _list.end();
12344     --liter;
12345     _remove( liter->first );
12346    }
12347   }
12348 
12349 
12350 
12351 
12352   inline const Key_List get_all_keys( void ) {
12353    ;
12354    Key_List ret;
12355    for( List_cIter liter = _list.begin(); liter != _list.end(); liter++ )
12356     ret.push_back( liter->first );
12357    return ret;
12358   }
12359 
12360  private:
12361 
12362 
12363 
12364 
12365   inline Map_Iter _touch( const Key &key ) {
12366    Map_Iter miter = _index.find( key );
12367    if( miter == _index.end() ) return miter;
12368 
12369    _list.splice( _list.begin(), _list, miter->second );
12370    return miter;
12371   }
12372 
12373 
12374 
12375 
12376 
12377   inline void _remove( const Map_Iter &miter ) {
12378    _curr_size -= Sizefn()( miter->second->second );
12379    _list.erase( miter->second );
12380    _index.erase( miter );
12381   }
12382 
12383 
12384 
12385 
12386   inline void _remove( const Key &key ) {
12387    Map_Iter miter = _index.find( key );
12388    _remove( miter );
12389   }

12963   template <class _ForwardIterator, class _Tp>
12964     class raw_storage_iterator
12965     : public iterator<output_iterator_tag, void, void, void, void>
12966     {
12967     protected:
12968       _ForwardIterator _M_iter;
12969 
12970     public:
12971       explicit
12972       raw_storage_iterator(_ForwardIterator __x)
12973       : _M_iter(__x) {}
12974 
12975       raw_storage_iterator&
12976       operator*() { return *this; }
12977 
12978       raw_storage_iterator&
12979       operator=(const _Tp& __element)
12980       {
12981  std::_Construct(&*_M_iter, __element);
12982  return *this;
12983       }
12984 
12985       raw_storage_iterator<_ForwardIterator, _Tp>&
12986       operator++()
12987       {
12988  ++_M_iter;
12989  return *this;
12990       }
12991 
12992       raw_storage_iterator<_ForwardIterator, _Tp>
12993       operator++(int)
12994       {
12995  raw_storage_iterator<_ForwardIterator, _Tp> __tmp = *this;
12996  ++_M_iter;
12997  return __tmp;
12998       }
12999     };

15633     bool
15634     __is_heap(_RandomAccessIterator __first, _Distance __n)
15635     {
15636       _Distance __parent = 0;
15637       for (_Distance __child = 1; __child < __n; ++__child)
15638  {
15639    if (__first[__parent] < __first[__child])
15640      return false;
15641    if ((__child & 1) == 0)
15642      ++__parent;
15643  }
15644       return true;
15645     }

15750     void
15751     __adjust_heap(_RandomAccessIterator __first, _Distance __holeIndex,
15752     _Distance __len, _Tp __value)
15753     {

17286     void
17287     __rotate(_RandomAccessIterator __first,
17288       _RandomAccessIterator __middle,
17289       _RandomAccessIterator __last,
17290       random_access_iterator_tag)
17291     {
17292 
17293      
17294 
17295 
17296       if (__first == __middle || __last == __middle)

17298

17300  _Distance;
17301       typedef typename iterator_traits<_RandomAccessIterator>::value_type
17302  _ValueType;
17303 
17304       const _Distance __n = __last - __first;
17305       const _Distance __k = __middle - __first;
17306       const _Distance __l = __n - __k;
17307 
17308       if (__k == __l)
17309  {
17310    std::swap_ranges(__first, __middle, __middle);
17311    return;
17312  }
17313 
17314       const _Distance __d = __gcd(__n, __k);
17315 
17316       for (_Distance __i = 0; __i < __d; __i++)
17317  {
17318    _ValueType __tmp = *__first;
17319    _RandomAccessIterator __p = __first;
17320 
17321    if (__k < __l)
17322      {
17323        for (_Distance __j = 0; __j < __l / __d; __j++)

17325     if (__p > __first + __l)
17326       {
17327         *__p = *(__p - __l);
17328         __p -= __l;
17329       }
17330 
17331     *__p = *(__p + __k);
17332     __p += __k;
17333   }
17334      }
17335    else

17337        for (_Distance __j = 0; __j < __k / __d - 1; __j ++)
17338   {
17339     if (__p < __last - __k)
17340       {
17341         *__p = *(__p + __k);
17342         __p += __k;
17343       }
17344     *__p = * (__p - __l);
17345     __p -= __l;
17346   }

18033   template<typename _RandomAccessIterator, typename _Size>
18034     void
18035     __introsort_loop(_RandomAccessIterator __first,
18036        _RandomAccessIterator __last,
18037        _Size __depth_limit)
18038     {

18040  _ValueType;

18043  {
18044    if (__depth_limit == 0)
18045      {
18046        std::partial_sort(__first, __last, __last);
18047        return;
18048      }

18051      std::__unguarded_partition(__first, __last,
18052            _ValueType(std::__median(*__first,
18053         *(__first
18054           + (__last
18055              - __first)
18056           / 2),
18057         *(__last
18058           - 1))));
18059    std::__introsort_loop(__cut, __last, __depth_limit);
18060    __last = __cut;
18061  }
18062     }

18332       std::__merge_without_buffer(__first, __first_cut, __new_middle,
18333       __len11, __len22);

18828     typename _Compare>
18829     void
18830     __merge_adaptive(_BidirectionalIterator __first,
18831                      _BidirectionalIterator __middle,
18832        _BidirectionalIterator __last,
18833        _Distance __len1, _Distance __len2,
18834        _Pointer __buffer, _Distance __buffer_size,
18835        _Compare __comp)
18836     {
18837       if (__len1 <= __len2 && __len1 <= __buffer_size)
18838  {
18839    _Pointer __buffer_end = std::copy(__first, __middle, __buffer);
18840    std::merge(__buffer, __buffer_end, __middle, __last, __first, __comp);
18841  }

18843  {
18844    _Pointer __buffer_end = std::copy(__middle, __last, __buffer);
18845    std::__merge_backward(__first, __middle, __buffer, __buffer_end,
18846     __last, __comp);

18859            __comp);

18861      }

18866        __first_cut = std::upper_bound(__first, __middle, *__second_cut,
18867           __comp);
18868        __len11 = std::distance(__first, __first_cut);
18869      }

18871      std::__rotate_adaptive(__first_cut, __middle, __second_cut,
18872        __len1 - __len11, __len22, __buffer,
18873        __buffer_size);

18875     __len22, __buffer, __buffer_size, __comp);

19062     void
19063     __introselect(_RandomAccessIterator __first, _RandomAccessIterator __nth,
19064     _RandomAccessIterator __last, _Size __depth_limit)
19065     {
19066       typedef typename iterator_traits<_RandomAccessIterator>::value_type
19067  _ValueType;
19068 
19069       while (__last - __first > 3)
19070  {
19071    if (__depth_limit == 0)
19072      {
19073        std::__heap_select(__first, __nth + 1, __last);
19074 
19075        std::iter_swap(__first, __nth);
19076        return;
19077      }
19078    --__depth_limit;

19080      std::__unguarded_partition(__first, __last,

19089      __first = __cut;
19090    else
19091      __last = __cut;
19092  }
19093       std::__insertion_sort(__first, __last);
19094     }

20502      {
20503        ;

20522                _M_copy(__p, __s, __nleft);

20571     void

20584   template<typename _CharT, typename _Traits, typename _Alloc>
20585     void
20586     basic_string<_CharT, _Traits, _Alloc>::
20587     _M_mutate(size_type __pos, size_type __len1, size_type __len2)
20588     {
20589       const size_type __old_size = this->size();
20590       const size_type __new_size = __old_size + __len2 - __len1;
20591       const size_type __how_much = __old_size - __pos - __len1;
20592 
20593       if (__new_size > this->capacity() || _M_rep()->_M_is_shared())
20594  {
20595 
20596    const allocator_type __a = get_allocator();
20597    _Rep* __r = _Rep::_S_create(__new_size, this->capacity(), __a);
20598 
20599    if (__pos)
20600      _M_copy(__r->_M_refdata(), _M_data(), __pos);
20601    if (__how_much)
20602      _M_copy(__r->_M_refdata() + __pos + __len2,
20603       _M_data() + __pos + __len1, __how_much);
20604 
20605    _M_rep()->_M_dispose(__a);
20606    _M_data(__r->_M_refdata());
20607  }
20608       else if (__how_much && __len1 != __len2)
20609  {
20610 
20611    _M_move(_M_data() + __pos + __len2,
20612     _M_data() + __pos + __len1, __how_much);
20613  }
20614       _M_rep()->_M_set_length_and_sharable(__new_size);
20615     }

22545     streamsize
22546     basic_streambuf<_CharT, _Traits>::
22547     xsgetn(char_type* __s, streamsize __n)
22548     {
22549       streamsize __ret = 0;
22550       while (__ret < __n)
22551  {
22552    const streamsize __buf_len = this->egptr() - this->gptr();
22553    if (__buf_len)
22554      {
22555        const streamsize __remaining = __n - __ret;
22556        const streamsize __len = std::min(__buf_len, __remaining);
22557        traits_type::copy(__s, this->gptr(), __len);
22558        __ret += __len;
22559        __s += __len;
22560        this->gbump(__len);
22561      }
22562

22564      {
22565        const int_type __c = this->uflow();
22566        if (!traits_type::eq_int_type(__c, traits_type::eof()))
22567   {
22568     traits_type::assign(*__s++, traits_type::to_char_type(__c));
22569     ++__ret;
22570   }
22571        else
22572   break;
22573      }
22574  }
22575       return __ret;
22576     }

22579     streamsize
22580     basic_streambuf<_CharT, _Traits>::
22581     xsputn(const char_type* __s, streamsize __n)
22582     {
22583       streamsize __ret = 0;
22584       while (__ret < __n)
22585  {

22590        const streamsize __len = std::min(__buf_len, __remaining);
22591        traits_type::copy(this->pptr(), __s, __len);

22598      {
22599        int_type __c = this->overflow(traits_type::to_int_type(*__s));

22615   template<typename _CharT, typename _Traits>
22616     streamsize
22617     __copy_streambufs_eof(basic_streambuf<_CharT, _Traits>* __sbin,
22618      basic_streambuf<_CharT, _Traits>* __sbout,
22619      bool& __ineof)
22620     {
22621       streamsize __ret = 0;
22622       __ineof = true;
22623       typename _Traits::int_type __c = __sbin->sgetc();
22624       while (!_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, _Traits::eof()))
22625  {
22626    __c = __sbout->sputc(_Traits::to_char_type(__c));
22627    if (_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, _Traits::eof()))
22628      {
22629        __ineof = false;
22630        break;
22631      }
22632    ++__ret;
22633    __c = __sbin->snextc();
22634  }
22635       return __ret;
22636     }

24497      {
24498        if (__c >= _CharT2('0') && __c < _CharT2(_CharT2('0') + __len))

29057

29236     _CharT*

29238      const char* __gbeg, size_t __gsize,
29239      const _CharT* __first, const _CharT* __last)

31015       const __ctype_type& __ct = use_facet<__ctype_type>(__in.getloc());
31016       const __int_type __eof = _Traits::eof();
31017       __streambuf_type* __sb = __in.rdbuf();

31031     basic_istream<_CharT, _Traits>&
31032     operator>>(basic_istream<_CharT, _Traits>& __in,
31033         basic_string<_CharT, _Traits, _Alloc>& __str)
31034     {
31035       typedef basic_istream<_CharT, _Traits> __istream_type;
31036       typedef typename __istream_type::int_type __int_type;
31037       typedef typename __istream_type::__streambuf_type __streambuf_type;
31038       typedef typename __istream_type::__ctype_type __ctype_type;
31039       typedef basic_string<_CharT, _Traits, _Alloc> __string_type;
31040       typedef typename __string_type::size_type __size_type;
31041 
31042       __size_type __extracted = 0;
31043       ios_base::iostate __err = ios_base::iostate(ios_base::goodbit);
31044       typename __istream_type::sentry __cerb(__in, false);
31045       if (__cerb)
31046  {
31047    try
31048      {
31049 
31050        __str.erase();
31051        _CharT __buf[128];
31052        __size_type __len = 0;
31053        const streamsize __w = __in.width();
31054        const __size_type __n = __w > 0 ? static_cast<__size_type>(__w)
31055                                 : __str.max_size();
31056        const __ctype_type& __ct = use_facet<__ctype_type>(__in.getloc());
31057        const __int_type __eof = _Traits::eof();
31058        __streambuf_type* __sb = __in.rdbuf();
31059        __int_type __c = __sb->sgetc();
31060 
31061        while (__extracted < __n
31062        && !_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, __eof)
31063        && !__ct.is(ctype_base::space, _Traits::to_char_type(__c)))
31064   {
31065     if (__len == sizeof(__buf) / sizeof(_CharT))
31066       {
31067         __str.append(__buf, sizeof(__buf) / sizeof(_CharT));
31068         __len = 0;
31069       }
31070     __buf[__len++] = _Traits::to_char_type(__c);
31071     ++__extracted;
31072     __c = __sb->snextc();
31073   }
31074        __str.append(__buf, __len);
31075 
31076        if (_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, __eof))
31077   __err |= ios_base::eofbit;
31078        __in.width(0);
31079      }
31080    catch(...)
31081      {
31082 
31083 
31084 
31085        __in._M_setstate(ios_base::badbit);
31086      }
31087  }
31088 
31089       if (!__extracted)
31090  __err |= ios_base::failbit;
31091       if (__err)
31092  __in.setstate(__err);
31093       return __in;
31094     }

31096   template<typename _CharT, typename _Traits, typename _Alloc>
31097     basic_istream<_CharT, _Traits>&
31098     getline(basic_istream<_CharT, _Traits>& __in,
31099      basic_string<_CharT, _Traits, _Alloc>& __str, _CharT __delim)
31100     {
31101       typedef basic_istream<_CharT, _Traits> __istream_type;
31102       typedef typename __istream_type::int_type __int_type;
31103       typedef typename __istream_type::__streambuf_type __streambuf_type;
31104       typedef typename __istream_type::__ctype_type __ctype_type;
31105       typedef basic_string<_CharT, _Traits, _Alloc> __string_type;
31106       typedef typename __string_type::size_type __size_type;
31107 
31108       __size_type __extracted = 0;
31109       const __size_type __n = __str.max_size();
31110       ios_base::iostate __err = ios_base::iostate(ios_base::goodbit);
31111       typename __istream_type::sentry __cerb(__in, true);
31112       if (__cerb)
31113  {
31114    try
31115      {
31116        __str.erase();
31117        const __int_type __idelim = _Traits::to_int_type(__delim);
31118        const __int_type __eof = _Traits::eof();
31119        __streambuf_type* __sb = __in.rdbuf();
31120        __int_type __c = __sb->sgetc();
31121 
31122        while (__extracted < __n
31123        && !_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, __eof)
31124        && !_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, __idelim))
31125   {
31126     __str += _Traits::to_char_type(__c);
31127     ++__extracted;
31128     __c = __sb->snextc();
31129   }
31130 
31131        if (_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, __eof))
31132   __err |= ios_base::eofbit;
31133        else if (_Traits::eq_int_type(__c, __idelim))
31134   {
31135     ++__extracted;
31136     __sb->sbumpc();
31137   }
31138        else
31139   __err |= ios_base::failbit;
31140      }
31141    catch(...)
31142      {
31143 
31144 
31145 
31146        __in._M_setstate(ios_base::badbit);
31147      }
31148  }
31149       if (!__extracted)
31150  __err |= ios_base::failbit;
31151       if (__err)
31152  __in.setstate(__err);
31153       return __in;
31154     }
